data.description: Your backyard oasis awaits on a creek lot in walking distance to Boyd High school. The immaculately cared for home greets you with a sitting area as you enter the front door & office that could be a bonus bedroom as there is a closet. Formal dining & living room are open for a great family space. Backyard features a deck that looks out to a seasonal creek. A great place to unwind in your own space close to shopping & schools, this home is perfect for your escape from everyday stresses. Primary bedroom features a wall full of windows that look out to the backyard for relaxing natural light in the sitting area within. The primary bath features an amazing closet system, garden tub, & separate shower along with dual vanity. This single story home has an over-sized garage with room for a workbench & extra refrigerator or freezer. The roof was updated-replaced in 2018. Electric cooktop can be converted to natural gas with plumbing connection in place. Transferrable AHS Warranty in effect.
